{"tid":616994,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"歐聯六大經典入球~(包埋朗哥倒掛)","createTime":"2018-04-04T15:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T17:32:34.000Z","uid":785,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ea2b8f4bf42f68b23d8d2419458e68de8238dd7f","tid":616994,"uid":785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fmGdOYFwHsE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfmGdOYFwHsE&d=CSB0IGd1xZxngogkQDZv48n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=88621cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fmGdOYFwHsE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUEFA出左條短片，揾左六球經典入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..<br />\n最無印象係伊巴球勁BAN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..<br />\n我揀排第一位一定係拖舟果球斜身窩利，難度高之餘，仲要係決賽世界波，含金量極高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n文素基治球倒掛同朗哥倒掛分別在前者有用心控，後者直頭無控過，後者難度更高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美斯一扭幾個再入波好似已經係家常便飯，要算經典可以再搵其他入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFLORENZI球半場笠射，明顯係達史特根企得太出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人推介朗拿甸奴對車仔篤射都可以堪稱係經典<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9O3otJu2FWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9O3otJu2FWE&d=CSB0IGd1xZxngogkQDZv48n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b7fee848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9O3otJu2FWE</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n仲有無印象，有邊幾球歐聯入波係經典之餘，技術亦相當高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4c968de20883d409893945e67094a10e7f5022","tid":616994,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"思尼斯達絕殺車"},{"pid":"73b8336fdbcbfcea18450d619320542ea0ab5191","tid":616994,"uid":785,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ff4c968de20883d409893945e67094a10e7f5022","tid":616994,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"思尼斯達絕殺車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mg9PBpfTw9g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMg9PBpfTw9g&d=CSB0IGd1xZxngogkQDZv48n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bda467ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mg9PBpfTw9g</a><br />\n<br />\n難度唔係太高，絕殺時間比較深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0012cf36bfdaedce59a5345443368e5d93d5424f","tid":616994,"uid":43356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:00:26.000Z","msg":"巴哥頭鎚入妞亞個球又係好癲"},{"pid":"87c9bb0f296ac055c6e8a9de071e891cccf56da5","tid":616994,"uid":84834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"牙朗仲有球對波圖四十幾碼ban入都好深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4288a4ade4123d8740d48d0bf0901f7ce9211f","tid":616994,"uid":61829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"卡卡對最聯嗰球"},{"pid":"96ce040a8a34d42ded93371baef80d9630cb00ed","tid":616994,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff4c968de20883d409893945e67094a10e7f5022","tid":616994,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T15:51:29.000Z","msg":"思尼斯達絕殺車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"fucking disgrace<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e24cef259392f794f9a39220e65bc862e21f10","tid":616994,"uid":27785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"